{
  "stem": "11722.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we were no good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we, at the time, couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But as things went on, they finally-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] out of a close-knit family, the way I was brought up, I noticed the problems and the new rules that were being made against the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so, I was very concerned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think from then on in, we-- instead of becoming-- being normal, like normal kids wanting to do the things, we started-- I started thinking ahead and starting to fend for-- for my life and also for the lives of my younger brothers and especially my sister.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we were-- we became a little bit more serious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed away from anyone that was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't want to run into any kind of problems.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't want to create any problems for my dad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Children that age, they're very proud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they look up to their parents, that they can handle almost anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we just adhered to the-- to the things that my-- my parents told us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we started being withdrawn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later on, they-- they-- what they did is they were weakening our midst.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyone at a certain age, young men up to a certain age were being [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] called in-- into service.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it wasn't the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a work battalion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They called it in Hungarian, 'munkaszolgalat.' And they were sent away, probably to the front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I understand now we know that they were given shovels and picks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had to haul the ammunition and-- and-- and-- instead of giving them guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of those men never came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already in 1941, '42. 1941, '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
